WEBVTT

01:37.840 --> 01:41.100
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.160 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 25]

01:57.400 --> 01:58.350
Hello, Mr. Tan.

01:58.680 --> 01:59.479
We meet again.

01:59.509 --> 02:00.200
Mr. Ji.

02:00.510 --> 02:01.400
I'm really sorry

02:01.400 --> 02:02.280
to disturb you during work hours.

02:02.280 --> 02:02.870
Not at all.

02:02.870 --> 02:03.310
Please sit.

02:03.310 --> 02:03.640
Okay.

02:07.310 --> 02:09.830
Actually, I came here today on purpose

02:10.150 --> 02:11.360
because of something

02:11.360 --> 02:12.690
related to me yesterday

02:13.080 --> 02:15.000
that might drag Miss Xu Miyu

02:15.000 --> 02:16.530
into unnecessary trouble.

02:16.710 --> 02:18.890
Ms. Xu is a very important friend of mine.

02:18.890 --> 02:21.310
So I came to clear things up for her.

02:25.360 --> 02:27.150
Mr. Tan, you're willing to go
to great lengths for a friend.

02:27.150 --> 02:28.410
I can understand that.

02:28.430 --> 02:29.360
Rest assured.

02:29.390 --> 02:30.400
According to the hotel's regulations,

02:30.400 --> 02:31.800
if she didn't break any rules,

02:31.800 --> 02:33.150
we absolutely won't wrong her.

02:33.150 --> 02:33.840
Okay.

02:33.840 --> 02:37.240
But it's a fact that she caused
a negative impact on the hotel.

02:37.470 --> 02:39.270
We can only do things by the book.

02:39.840 --> 02:41.170
Then I'll make it short.

02:41.920 --> 02:44.360
I didn't stay in Room 1219 yesterday.

02:45.079 --> 02:46.800
After I settled Ms. Xu down,

02:46.800 --> 02:48.310
I went to Room 1810.

02:48.400 --> 02:50.120
I slept on the sofa
in the living room in my father's suite

02:50.120 --> 02:51.200
for the whole night.

02:51.200 --> 02:54.130
Of course, this is
the best solution I could think of.

02:54.150 --> 02:56.960
Then, Mr. Tan, have you ever thought

02:57.910 --> 02:59.400
that if you didn't interfere,

02:59.400 --> 03:01.170
things wouldn't be so complicated?

03:01.170 --> 03:05.350
[Purong Hotel]

03:05.320 --> 03:07.080
Mr. Ji, you think I'm being a busybody,

03:07.080 --> 03:07.710
don't you?

03:08.460 --> 03:10.260
Mr. Tan, you've misunderstood.

03:11.010 --> 03:12.050
What I mean is,

03:13.080 --> 03:14.680
you are also a public figure.

03:14.800 --> 03:16.829
You should know better than us

03:16.870 --> 03:18.310
how to avoid gossip.

03:19.290 --> 03:21.040
A hotel is full of gossip.

03:21.310 --> 03:22.520
This kind of rumor

03:22.790 --> 03:24.910
can be a fatal blow to someone.

03:25.130 --> 03:27.130
If you were there at the time, Mr. Ji,

03:27.340 --> 03:29.260
seeing Ms. Xu being
humiliated by her family

03:29.260 --> 03:30.870
and mocked by her colleagues,

03:30.870 --> 03:31.890
would you just stand by and do nothing?

03:31.890 --> 03:33.200
But I would never
take advantage of her vulnerability.

03:33.200 --> 03:34.040
What do you think,

03:34.040 --> 03:34.850
Mr. Tan?

03:37.570 --> 03:39.829
Mr. Ji, may I ask you
a question in return?

03:40.180 --> 03:41.430
In what capacity

03:41.430 --> 03:42.590
are you saying these things to me?

03:42.590 --> 03:43.980
And in what capacity

03:44.010 --> 03:46.540
are you approaching
an employee of our hotel?

03:56.110 --> 03:58.210
Mr. Ji, I think you've missed the point.

03:58.210 --> 03:59.960
Actually, what you should care about

03:59.960 --> 04:01.220
is why she got so drunk,

04:01.930 --> 04:03.710
what exactly she's been through,

04:03.710 --> 04:04.470
and how much she's endured

04:04.470 --> 04:06.120
that she shouldn't have.

04:06.140 --> 04:07.820
Don't focus on me.

04:08.630 --> 04:09.630
What do you think?

04:18.269 --> 04:19.709
Mr. Ji, I believe that

04:19.750 --> 04:21.450
for employees as precious as gold,

04:21.450 --> 04:23.980
just providing a shining stage
isn't enough.

04:24.180 --> 04:26.200
You must also be there
for them in their vulnerable moments.

04:26.200 --> 04:28.400
Of course, you have
a good eye for talent, Mr. Ji.

04:28.400 --> 04:30.460
You must understand this principle.

04:36.000 --> 04:37.120
I've also checked the surveillance.

04:37.120 --> 04:37.780
Indeed,

04:38.040 --> 04:39.630
Tan Jizhou stayed in room 1219

04:39.630 --> 04:41.490
for less than 5 minutes
before coming out.

04:41.490 --> 04:42.310
Two minutes later,

04:42.310 --> 04:45.030
he appeared in the corridor
of the executive floor.

04:45.030 --> 04:46.070
He wasn't seen on camera again

04:46.070 --> 04:47.190
until around 8:40

04:47.190 --> 04:49.270
the next morning.

04:50.600 --> 04:52.630
I indirectly asked Mr. Tan Sr. about it.

04:52.630 --> 04:53.480
It's true...

04:59.870 --> 05:00.670
Hello, Mr. Ji.

05:00.720 --> 05:01.600
Hello, Mr. Xue.

05:01.600 --> 05:03.040
What are you whispering about?

05:03.040 --> 05:03.920
Nothing.

05:03.940 --> 05:04.770
Sorry, Mr. Ji.

05:08.480 --> 05:09.240
Bro,

05:09.590 --> 05:11.230
are you out of your mind?

05:11.430 --> 05:12.920
You want to be a tyrant?

05:15.930 --> 05:16.760
This way.

05:24.190 --> 05:24.950
Okay.

05:24.950 --> 05:25.830
Here.

05:27.160 --> 05:28.040
Xiaoyan.

05:28.750 --> 05:30.310
Do you think our complaint

05:30.340 --> 05:31.950
will backfire?

05:32.190 --> 05:34.140
Look at her, acting like nothing happened

05:34.140 --> 05:36.090
after coming out of Mr. Ji's office.

05:36.090 --> 05:38.970
Xu Miyu staying in
a guest's room late at night

05:39.000 --> 05:40.560
is an undeniable fact.

05:40.590 --> 05:42.790
We have it all recorded in the computer.

05:43.370 --> 05:44.159
But that doesn't mean

05:44.159 --> 05:45.760
they actually did anything.

05:45.770 --> 05:46.630
It doesn't matter.

05:46.630 --> 05:48.670
Giving people cause
for gossip is unacceptable.

05:48.670 --> 05:50.190
How can a lobby manager

05:50.210 --> 05:51.659
be so frivolous?

05:52.240 --> 05:53.000
If word gets out,

05:53.000 --> 05:54.750
it'll ruin our hotel's image.

05:55.330 --> 05:57.820
You guys really don't get it.

05:59.420 --> 06:00.070
No.

06:00.270 --> 06:02.730
I have to go talk
to Director Bai again later.

06:02.730 --> 06:03.510
After all this,

06:03.510 --> 06:04.630
we still can't bring her down.

06:04.630 --> 06:05.830
Is there no justice?

06:08.160 --> 06:08.750
Come in.

06:11.830 --> 06:12.310
Mr. Ji,

06:12.380 --> 06:13.580
Director Bai is here.

06:13.630 --> 06:14.430
Show him in.

06:16.770 --> 06:18.620
Mr. Ji, you were looking for me?

06:18.650 --> 06:19.450
Director Bai.

06:20.600 --> 06:22.360
I heard you're very anxious to know

06:22.360 --> 06:26.420
the investigation results of Ms. Xu
staying overnight in the guest room.

06:26.710 --> 06:27.950
Not really.

06:27.970 --> 06:30.030
They're just rumors among the staff.

06:31.250 --> 06:33.450
The matter has been
thoroughly investigated.

06:33.450 --> 06:35.300
Ms. Xu is not involved in any violations.

06:35.300 --> 06:37.760
There will be no administrative penalties.

06:37.860 --> 06:39.180
No punishment at all?

06:40.360 --> 06:42.320
Mr. Ji, you might not
have heard the rumors.

06:42.320 --> 06:45.180
It's said the scene was extremely indecent

06:45.210 --> 06:46.250
and unsightly.

06:46.550 --> 06:48.640
Did you see it with your own eyes?

06:48.670 --> 06:49.340
No.

06:49.360 --> 06:52.040
But the rumor is all over the place today.

06:52.070 --> 06:54.440
Everyone is saying
that the lobby manager of our Front Office

06:54.440 --> 06:56.880
got drunk and stayed in a guest's room.

06:57.110 --> 06:58.210
This has a very negative impact.

06:58.210 --> 07:00.970
I'm mainly afraid that the young girls
in the Front Office

07:00.970 --> 07:01.950
will follow her example.

07:01.950 --> 07:03.950
It will be hard to manage them later.

07:03.970 --> 07:05.060
Didn't you just say

07:05.090 --> 07:07.620
that the subordinates
love to spread rumors?

07:07.800 --> 07:09.530
That is indeed the case.

07:09.560 --> 07:11.210
A wise man does not believe rumors.

07:11.210 --> 07:12.010
Director Bai.

07:12.320 --> 07:14.560
Your department's employees
complained to you.

07:14.560 --> 07:16.560
What investigations have you done?

07:16.770 --> 07:18.260
I haven't yet...

07:18.290 --> 07:20.750
Have you checked the hotel's surveillance?

07:20.950 --> 07:21.310
No.

07:21.310 --> 07:22.730
Have you asked the person involved?

07:22.730 --> 07:23.460
No.

07:23.490 --> 07:25.690
Spreading rumors without evidence

07:25.800 --> 07:27.800
is a clear violation of hotel rules.

07:27.830 --> 07:28.480
Also,

07:29.160 --> 07:30.890
this complaint letter of yours

07:30.950 --> 07:34.630
states that Xu Miyu spent the night
with a guest in his room.

07:34.770 --> 07:36.570
It's written in black and white.

07:36.790 --> 07:39.450
If we look into it
and it doesn't match the facts,

07:39.510 --> 07:41.909
every single person who signed this

07:41.930 --> 07:43.770
will have to bear legal responsibility.

07:43.770 --> 07:45.290
What is this?

07:46.190 --> 07:48.520
These people do things without thinking.

07:48.950 --> 07:50.040
Without any evidence,

07:50.040 --> 07:51.040
and without reporting to their superiors,

07:51.040 --> 07:52.500
they came straight to you.

07:53.490 --> 07:54.430
Seriously.

07:56.250 --> 07:58.780
So you were kept
in the dark too, Director Bai?

07:58.790 --> 08:00.810
Yes, I was misled by them.

08:01.280 --> 08:01.790
Mr. Ji.

08:02.050 --> 08:03.920
Since you've investigated clearly,

08:03.920 --> 08:06.080
and Ms. Xu was indeed wronged,

08:06.190 --> 08:07.960
I'll go back
and give them a good talking-to.

08:07.960 --> 08:09.430
Director Bai, if you can't handle it,

08:09.430 --> 08:10.960
you can leave it to us.

08:11.320 --> 08:12.450
I... I can handle it.

08:13.250 --> 08:15.290
You don't need to
step in for such a small matter.

08:15.290 --> 08:16.440
Rest assured, Mr. Ji.

08:16.440 --> 08:17.680
I know what to do.

08:17.700 --> 08:18.580
I promise

08:18.760 --> 08:20.360
that today's rumors

08:20.800 --> 08:22.290
will turn into a gust of wind

08:22.290 --> 08:23.410
and blow far away.

08:23.960 --> 08:26.640
Then I'll trouble you to take the lead

08:26.660 --> 08:28.320
and set a good example
for the Front Office.

08:28.320 --> 08:29.560
Yes, yes, Mr. Ji.

08:39.840 --> 08:40.630
Lu Xiaoyan,

08:40.929 --> 08:42.570
have you finished your situation report?

08:42.570 --> 08:43.210
No.

08:43.480 --> 08:44.440
Why not?

08:45.960 --> 08:47.860
You haven't even cleaned up your own mess,

08:47.860 --> 08:49.980
and you're asking me about my report?

08:50.100 --> 08:51.050
Who do you think you are?

08:51.050 --> 08:52.360
I'm your boss,

08:52.440 --> 08:54.110
and you made a mistake at work.

08:57.000 --> 08:59.400
My superior will handle my problems.

08:59.520 --> 09:01.480
Please give me the report now.

09:01.500 --> 09:02.380
I won't.

09:03.050 --> 09:04.850
What are you going to do about it?

09:05.420 --> 09:06.130
Do you want to know?

09:06.130 --> 09:06.960
Yes.

09:09.070 --> 09:09.760
Ying.

09:10.050 --> 09:11.280
Give me the performance appraisal form.

09:11.280 --> 09:12.160
Okay, Ma'am.

09:17.880 --> 09:19.200
I've deducted 20 points
from your monthly performance.

09:19.200 --> 09:20.320
If you don't submit it tomorrow,

09:20.320 --> 09:21.580
I'll deduct 30 points.

09:21.860 --> 09:22.620
You...

09:23.920 --> 09:24.770
Director Bai!

09:25.020 --> 09:25.630
Director Bai,

09:25.630 --> 09:27.440
please come and judge for us!

09:28.510 --> 09:29.320
Director Bai.

09:30.270 --> 09:30.960
Ms. Xu.

09:30.980 --> 09:31.850
It's lunch break.

09:31.850 --> 09:32.970
Haven't you gone to eat?

09:32.970 --> 09:34.950
I'll go after I handle this.

09:35.040 --> 09:36.930
Director Bai, look at Ms. Xu.

09:36.960 --> 09:38.080
She is crazy today.

09:38.150 --> 09:39.270
Her own behavior is improper,

09:39.270 --> 09:40.750
yet she deducts 20 points from me.

09:40.750 --> 09:42.530
Will you leaders do something about it?

09:42.530 --> 09:43.840
And with so many of us

09:43.920 --> 09:45.700
signing the complaint letter,

09:45.750 --> 09:47.980
will the general manager even read it?

09:48.080 --> 09:49.270
You little girls,

09:49.270 --> 09:51.530
I haven't settled the score with you yet.

09:51.580 --> 09:53.890
What complaint letter?

09:53.920 --> 09:55.750
What nonsense are you all making?

09:55.750 --> 09:57.150
Whatever Ms. Xu does

09:57.150 --> 09:58.520
is none of your business.

09:58.520 --> 09:59.780
As for you, Lu Xiaoyan,

09:59.930 --> 10:02.300
I haven't punished you for yesterday.

10:03.030 --> 10:04.890
Get your self-criticism written now.

10:04.890 --> 10:05.960
Write down the whole process

10:05.960 --> 10:07.800
clearly and seriously.

10:07.820 --> 10:09.620
Hand it in today once you finish.

10:13.470 --> 10:15.400
She should hand it in to you, right?

10:16.370 --> 10:17.830
Let Ms. Xu review it.

10:17.900 --> 10:19.170
If you don't finish it today,

10:19.170 --> 10:20.770
don't come to work tomorrow.

10:21.230 --> 10:22.110
Did you hear me?

10:22.920 --> 10:24.040
All of you,

10:24.070 --> 10:25.710
starting today,

10:25.740 --> 10:28.970
if anyone thinks
they are smart and talks nonsense,

10:28.990 --> 10:30.470
or passes notes,

10:30.510 --> 10:31.760
I'm warning you,

10:32.100 --> 10:33.620
I won't protect you.

10:37.630 --> 10:39.630
Ms. Xu, go have lunch.

10:40.180 --> 10:41.410
When she finishes the self-criticism,

10:41.410 --> 10:42.540
have her come to you.

10:42.670 --> 10:44.270
It has to pass your approval.

10:44.360 --> 10:45.740
If you are not satisfied,

10:45.740 --> 10:46.870
make her rewrite it.

10:47.190 --> 10:48.560
Thank you, Director Bai.

10:48.560 --> 10:50.310
Thank you for your support.

10:50.340 --> 10:51.390
It's my duty.

10:51.530 --> 10:52.560
I'll go eat now.

10:59.150 --> 11:00.480
Director Bai.

11:00.750 --> 11:01.120
She...

11:01.120 --> 11:02.310
Don't point.

11:02.340 --> 11:04.080
Hurry up and write.

11:05.750 --> 11:07.480
A bunch of troublesome girls.

11:14.910 --> 11:15.750
Mr. Ji.

11:16.160 --> 11:16.920
Morning.

11:38.550 --> 11:40.070
I recently discovered

11:40.090 --> 11:42.570
life is just a series of disappointments.

11:44.270 --> 11:45.950
What do you think of this?

11:46.510 --> 11:48.360
This is so impressive.

11:49.070 --> 11:51.870
I actually really want to transfer Ya
to the Western restaurant.

11:51.870 --> 11:54.270
But look at Bao's skills.

11:54.270 --> 11:55.730
She really can't compare.

11:56.030 --> 11:57.510
Ya's knife skills are excellent.

11:57.510 --> 11:59.270
Isn't it good for her
to be in the Chinese restaurant?

11:59.270 --> 12:00.390
She doesn't like it.

12:00.390 --> 12:01.790
She just wants to make cakes.

12:01.790 --> 12:04.050
Things just don't go as planned, do they?

12:06.360 --> 12:07.720
Did you make this?

12:08.270 --> 12:09.510
I just made it for fun.

12:10.810 --> 12:12.420
Let me steam it.

12:16.100 --> 12:17.380
What about Ya?

12:18.150 --> 12:19.150
Ya?

12:19.670 --> 12:21.670
I can only tell her
to let nature take its course,

12:21.670 --> 12:24.190
and keep working with me
at the Chinese restaurant.

12:24.190 --> 12:26.070
You should also let things be.

12:26.090 --> 12:28.030
There are many things
you simply can't control.

12:28.030 --> 12:29.790
As for those baseless rumors,

12:29.840 --> 12:31.290
just ignore them.

12:31.310 --> 12:33.010
What's the worst that could happen?

12:33.010 --> 12:35.450
At most, it reaches Mr. Ji's office.

12:35.550 --> 12:37.280
Mr. Ji will swat them

12:37.300 --> 12:38.450
all like flies.

12:40.950 --> 12:43.060
They've sent me
this joint compliant letter.

12:43.060 --> 12:44.270
Of course, I could

12:44.830 --> 12:45.840
suppress it

12:46.180 --> 12:48.550
and keep you in your position
against broad objection.

12:48.550 --> 12:49.900
But why should I do that?

12:50.980 --> 12:51.910
Are you worth it?

12:56.290 --> 12:58.040
Did he bully you again?

12:59.510 --> 13:01.290
He is the general manager.

13:01.320 --> 13:03.410
There is really nothing between us.

13:03.430 --> 13:05.030
Stop always trying

13:05.060 --> 13:06.770
to pair us up.

13:07.790 --> 13:08.670
Okay.

13:08.670 --> 13:09.750
I'll stop talking.

13:10.630 --> 13:12.680
Then don't look so sad.

13:12.870 --> 13:13.670
Smile a little.

13:13.670 --> 13:15.030
Cheer up, okay?

13:17.600 --> 13:19.030
That looks terrible.

13:23.270 --> 13:25.330
You know how to make corn out of dough?

13:28.010 --> 13:29.360
What else can you make?

13:29.390 --> 13:31.120
I can also make little monkeys.

13:31.910 --> 13:32.750
Wait.

13:45.250 --> 13:46.710
They are all a bit lacking.

13:47.750 --> 13:49.180
Kuanli has been interfering,

13:49.180 --> 13:50.610
making it hard to find

13:51.630 --> 13:53.360
good pastry chefs in this city.

13:54.030 --> 13:55.440
We've made appointments with so many

13:55.440 --> 13:56.550
foreign Michelin chefs.

13:56.550 --> 13:57.680
You've met them all,

13:57.800 --> 13:59.390
but you're not satisfied with any of them.

13:59.390 --> 14:01.510
We can't just look at titles and sales.

14:01.510 --> 14:02.270
Most importantly,

14:02.270 --> 14:03.750
they have to match the style

14:03.750 --> 14:05.480
and character of Purong Hotel.

14:05.510 --> 14:07.630
Just like that Yan Du Xian from before.

14:07.630 --> 14:09.120
As for the style of Purong Hotel,

14:09.120 --> 14:10.910
it's the old Shanghai flavor.

14:12.400 --> 14:14.760
For example, the almond pastries

14:15.120 --> 14:16.150
and eclairs from Harbin Food Factory,

14:16.150 --> 14:18.170
and the palmiers from Park Hotel.

14:18.190 --> 14:20.430
That field is way too competitive.

14:21.480 --> 14:24.150
Should we offer
Chinese-style afternoon tea?

14:24.750 --> 14:26.480
Chinese-style afternoon tea?

14:26.550 --> 14:27.360
Look.

14:27.790 --> 14:29.720
Think about how many milk tea brands

14:29.720 --> 14:31.390
are moving into Chinese tea now.

14:31.390 --> 14:32.790
The lines for Shen Dacheng's Qingtuan

14:32.790 --> 14:34.390
and Laodafang's Suzhou-style mooncakes

14:34.390 --> 14:35.870
are so long.

14:35.890 --> 14:36.630
That's enough to show

14:36.630 --> 14:39.840
that the market for Chinese pastries
is not to be underestimated.

14:39.840 --> 14:41.320
Besides, our Chinese restaurant

14:41.320 --> 14:42.750
is currently trending.

14:42.870 --> 14:45.510
Rather than crowding
into the Western dessert market,

14:45.510 --> 14:46.370
we might as well

14:46.630 --> 14:48.030
use Chinese tea snacks

14:48.050 --> 14:49.530
to make a breakthrough.

14:59.030 --> 15:00.440
Come help.

15:14.000 --> 15:14.720
Mr. Bao.

15:14.740 --> 15:16.340
Please introduce this to us.

15:18.580 --> 15:19.930
This half is Chinese-style.

15:19.930 --> 15:21.530
That half is Western-style.

15:26.270 --> 15:27.480
Mr. Ji. Mr. Guo.

15:27.480 --> 15:28.750
Mr. Xue. This apprentice of mine

15:28.750 --> 15:31.520
is clumsy with words. He knows how to do
the job, just not how to explain it.

15:31.520 --> 15:33.180
Like these today,

15:33.630 --> 15:35.600
we have both Chinese and Western styles.

15:35.600 --> 15:38.000
Mr. Bao's concept is
to embrace a mix of cultures.

15:38.000 --> 15:40.200
It centers on Chinese desserts,

15:40.270 --> 15:42.120
paired with Italian, Japanese,

15:42.120 --> 15:44.240
and British classics,

15:44.360 --> 15:46.760
to create
a cultural exchange on the plate.

15:51.000 --> 15:52.630
As for the Chinese desserts,

15:52.670 --> 15:54.600
are there any other new creations?

15:58.390 --> 15:59.450
Take a look at this,

16:00.000 --> 16:01.600
the Rainbow Mille-Feuille.

16:02.290 --> 16:03.650
This looks good.

16:04.780 --> 16:05.610
Let me try it.

16:11.170 --> 16:12.100
It's delicious.

16:13.630 --> 16:14.480
However,

16:14.870 --> 16:15.960
Xinlong Hotel

16:15.960 --> 16:18.620
is also making
the Four Seasons Mille-Feuille.

16:18.630 --> 16:20.000
If we make it too,

16:21.170 --> 16:22.770
it would be too competitive.

16:23.840 --> 16:24.670
But of course,

16:24.670 --> 16:26.000
if there are no other options,

16:26.000 --> 16:27.630
we can try this first.

16:27.920 --> 16:29.120
Wait a minute, Mr. Ji.

16:29.730 --> 16:31.280
I have a hidden item here.

16:32.640 --> 16:34.430
What secret weapon are you hiding?

16:34.430 --> 16:35.280
Bring it out.

16:35.300 --> 16:36.260
You said it.

16:49.240 --> 16:50.720
Very good.

16:51.630 --> 16:52.630
Who made this?

16:54.510 --> 16:55.790
Xu Miyu.

17:03.260 --> 17:04.410
Okay, are you ready?

17:04.440 --> 17:05.200
Ready.

17:07.089 --> 17:08.880
Okay, change your pose for another one.

17:08.880 --> 17:10.609
Fix your hair. It's a bit messy.

17:13.000 --> 17:13.900
[Mom]

17:16.369 --> 17:17.329
Here we go.

17:17.880 --> 17:20.400
Three, two, one.

17:20.930 --> 17:21.680
Alright.

17:21.710 --> 17:22.690
Here, take a look.

17:22.690 --> 17:23.710
Thank you.

17:28.210 --> 17:30.000
Hello, Mom. I'm working right now.

17:30.000 --> 17:31.060
What's the matter?

17:32.270 --> 17:34.130
Working overtime on the weekend?

17:34.930 --> 17:36.300
It's just an excuse.

17:36.430 --> 17:38.400
Whenever she doesn't want
to answer the phone,

17:38.400 --> 17:39.670
she is always busy.

17:41.150 --> 17:44.530
Miyu, I'm calling you for a reason.

17:45.640 --> 17:48.160
We are family,
so I'll skip the pleasantries.

17:48.160 --> 17:51.230
How much money do you
have left in your bank account?

17:52.000 --> 17:52.790
Hello?

17:53.410 --> 17:54.540
Are you listening?

17:59.730 --> 18:00.620
Mom.

18:01.600 --> 18:03.990
I still have to pay off
my debts every month.

18:03.990 --> 18:07.390
Ms. Xu, the Chinese restaurant's kitchen
is looking for you.

18:07.870 --> 18:09.400
Got it. I'll be right there.

18:09.890 --> 18:10.750
Mom, I have work to do.

18:10.750 --> 18:11.810
I'm hanging up now.

18:17.420 --> 18:18.180
Hello?

18:23.450 --> 18:24.550
She is busy.

18:24.570 --> 18:25.230
She hung up.

18:26.560 --> 18:28.360
Dad, what are you doing?

18:28.380 --> 18:29.380
Are you okay?

18:30.850 --> 18:31.850
See for yourself.

18:32.700 --> 18:34.070
In the past,

18:34.090 --> 18:35.120
even if you gave her
all the courage in the world,

18:35.120 --> 18:36.360
she wouldn't dare.

18:36.590 --> 18:37.790
Now look at her.

18:38.070 --> 18:39.550
Staying in a big city,

18:39.570 --> 18:40.920
living in a grand hotel.

18:40.950 --> 18:42.440
Now that she's divorced,

18:42.700 --> 18:44.900
she's doing great.

18:44.930 --> 18:45.820
What about us?

18:47.220 --> 18:49.250
We didn't get anything at all.

18:49.520 --> 18:50.980
We're the ones losing out.

18:54.500 --> 18:55.150
Xiumei.

18:55.380 --> 18:57.390
If she hangs up, call again.

18:57.410 --> 18:58.300
Keep calling.

18:58.330 --> 19:00.090
Call until she answers.

19:00.110 --> 19:00.910
Okay.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.400
And you.

19:02.620 --> 19:03.160
[Call]

19:03.250 --> 19:04.150
[Miyu]

19:04.320 --> 19:06.560
You don't even know your own limits.

19:06.980 --> 19:09.440
Why did you enroll Man
in an international school?

19:09.440 --> 19:11.200
Why are you scolding me?

19:11.540 --> 19:14.470
Which parent doesn't
do everything for their child?

19:22.720 --> 19:23.400
Hello, Mom.

19:23.590 --> 19:24.630
Miyu,

19:24.650 --> 19:26.450
you finally answered the phone.

19:26.720 --> 19:29.200
I really couldn't go on otherwise.

19:29.830 --> 19:32.060
Mom, my life isn't easy either.

19:32.080 --> 19:33.090
I understand you,

19:33.140 --> 19:35.630
but I'm fighting all alone in Shanghai.

19:36.070 --> 19:38.360
Have you ever asked me how I'm doing?

19:38.480 --> 19:40.650
I really have no choice.

19:42.530 --> 19:44.030
Mom, I have no choice either.

19:44.030 --> 19:45.100
I can't help you.

19:45.620 --> 19:46.510
I'm sorry.

19:52.310 --> 19:53.910
Did something happen to you?

19:54.710 --> 19:56.250
No. You're looking for me?

19:58.200 --> 19:58.920
Let's go.

20:20.530 --> 20:21.530
Let me make a corn.

20:59.240 --> 21:00.160
Have a taste.

21:01.080 --> 21:04.010
You've learned to make
Suzhou-style boat pastries?

21:04.320 --> 21:05.980
I didn't learn it systematically.

21:05.980 --> 21:08.060
I just picked it up from watching.

21:08.820 --> 21:10.820
They're just okay for a casual bite.

21:11.200 --> 21:12.660
Who taught you?

21:12.690 --> 21:13.990
My mom taught me.

21:14.560 --> 21:16.890
She only taught me
to make these few types.

21:17.160 --> 21:20.290
You mean your mom knows more?

21:20.330 --> 21:21.240
Yes.

21:21.780 --> 21:22.980
When my mom was young,

21:23.000 --> 21:25.170
she learned from a master in town.

21:25.200 --> 21:26.400
Every Chinese New Year, she also

21:26.400 --> 21:28.530
makes some in different shapes for us.

21:28.880 --> 21:31.210
She can even make Chinese zodiac animals.

21:34.150 --> 21:35.240
How about this?

21:35.350 --> 21:37.270
We'd like to invite your mother

21:37.270 --> 21:38.810
to come to Purong Hotel.

21:39.700 --> 21:40.880
We just want to observe

21:40.880 --> 21:42.070
her boat pastries craftsmanship.

21:42.070 --> 21:43.160
There's no pressure.

21:43.160 --> 21:44.880
We just want her to come over

21:44.880 --> 21:45.640
and talk it through with us.

21:45.640 --> 21:47.810
If there's really
an opportunity for cooperation,

21:47.810 --> 21:50.000
we'd be happy to see it happen.

21:59.200 --> 22:00.720
If I had any other way,

22:00.720 --> 22:02.640
I wouldn't come begging you.

22:01.660 --> 22:05.940
[Staff Only]

22:02.940 --> 22:06.030
Your sister is rummaging
through the house right now.

22:07.130 --> 22:08.430
Mom, do you still want the money?

22:08.430 --> 22:10.320
Yes, of course I do.

22:10.550 --> 22:11.350
Do you have it?

22:11.440 --> 22:13.760
If you want the money,
come here right now.

22:13.760 --> 22:17.560
[Staff Only]

22:19.190 --> 22:21.110
Your sister just finished tormenting you.

22:21.110 --> 22:23.000
Now you've brought your mom here.

22:23.030 --> 22:26.230
You really don't mind
the trouble your family brings you.

22:26.290 --> 22:28.120
Actually, I was quite hesitant at first.

22:28.120 --> 22:29.320
But then I thought,

22:29.340 --> 22:31.500
instead of having them
wait for me to feed them every day,

22:31.500 --> 22:33.870
it's better to let them
find their own way out.

22:33.870 --> 22:35.550
Actually, my mom's skills

22:35.570 --> 22:36.960
are really quite amazing.

22:36.960 --> 22:39.500
It's just that she didn't have
a chance to show them off before.

22:39.500 --> 22:41.130
The hotel happens to need it this time,

22:41.130 --> 22:42.590
so I wanted to give her a chance

22:42.590 --> 22:45.080
to discover her own value.

22:45.190 --> 22:46.520
She shouldn't always entrust her life

22:46.520 --> 22:47.850
to someone else.

22:47.960 --> 22:49.850
That's a really nice thought.

22:49.870 --> 22:51.410
But knowing your mom's personality,

22:51.410 --> 22:52.520
once she's here,

22:52.550 --> 22:53.640
you won't be able to control her at all.

22:53.640 --> 22:55.630
She'll cause trouble
for you all over the hotel.

22:55.630 --> 22:57.130
It absolutely won't happen this time.

22:57.130 --> 22:58.800
I've already laid down the rules with her.

22:58.800 --> 23:00.290
The hotel has its rules.

23:00.310 --> 23:03.640
If she can't accept them,
she'll have to leave immediately.

23:04.680 --> 23:06.250
Did you really say that?

23:07.070 --> 23:08.880
Not bad, Xu Miyu.

23:08.880 --> 23:10.200
You're getting tough now.

23:10.200 --> 23:12.460
With you backing me up,
who am I afraid of?

23:12.720 --> 23:13.240
Let's go.

23:13.240 --> 23:13.830
Let's go.

23:19.030 --> 23:19.770
Mr. Ji.

23:21.070 --> 23:22.110
I have something else to do.

23:22.110 --> 23:23.160
I'll get going.

23:23.660 --> 23:24.590
Qiaoqi.

23:29.640 --> 23:31.450
The desserts you made

23:31.590 --> 23:33.990
are not only beautiful but also delicious.

23:34.170 --> 23:35.170
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

23:38.240 --> 23:39.970
About what happened last time,

23:40.120 --> 23:41.400
I misunderstood you.

23:41.550 --> 23:44.280
And I said those nonsensical things.

23:44.640 --> 23:45.470
What things?

23:47.110 --> 23:49.690
Like whether you are worth it or not.

23:54.710 --> 23:57.270
I shouldn't meddle
in your private affairs.

23:57.310 --> 23:58.590
Whether it's worth it or not

23:58.590 --> 24:00.210
is not my place to judge.

24:01.050 --> 24:02.780
So I apologize to you.

24:03.110 --> 24:03.790
I'm sorry.

24:06.400 --> 24:08.400
You don't need to apologize, Mr. Ji.

24:08.790 --> 24:09.850
You have your standpoint,

24:09.850 --> 24:12.110
and I also did something inappropriate.

24:12.240 --> 24:13.790
If there's nothing else,

24:14.140 --> 24:15.100
I'll get going.

24:15.360 --> 24:16.010
Miyu.

24:18.590 --> 24:19.640
Are you still angry with me?

24:19.640 --> 24:20.310
Yes.

24:20.490 --> 24:21.590
I am angry.

24:22.210 --> 24:24.090
I do not want to be the kind of person

24:24.090 --> 24:25.640
who forgives the moment
someone says sorry.

24:25.640 --> 24:26.440
Is that okay?

24:27.750 --> 24:28.510
It is.

24:29.310 --> 24:30.170
Of course it is.

25:00.800 --> 25:02.500
Isn't this Chef Li?

25:02.530 --> 25:04.090
Why are you getting off work so late?

25:04.090 --> 25:06.290
Where did you go to save the world again?

25:06.640 --> 25:08.350
Mr. Duan Jr.,
with you not at the hotel today,

25:08.350 --> 25:10.700
the world feels unusually peaceful.

25:14.260 --> 25:16.380
Do you know how to talk properly?

25:22.270 --> 25:23.640
I heard Mr. Ji

25:23.640 --> 25:27.040
has been thinking about
improving the afternoon tea lately.

25:27.720 --> 25:29.640
The stuff your restaurant makes

25:29.640 --> 25:31.370
is even more choking than dirt.

25:31.750 --> 25:32.830
Give it up.

25:33.410 --> 25:35.150
You've already turned
the Chinese restaurant around.

25:35.150 --> 25:37.550
Don't end up dragging
the Western one down.

25:37.770 --> 25:39.450
Don't you worry about that.

25:39.680 --> 25:41.780
Mr. Ji has his secret weapon.

25:41.840 --> 25:43.370
What secret weapon?

25:43.640 --> 25:44.920
No comment.

25:46.880 --> 25:49.160
Is it that hard to admit defeat?

25:50.690 --> 25:52.550
What do you say? Care to make a bet?

25:53.200 --> 25:54.530
Within a month,

25:54.550 --> 25:55.880
Purong's afternoon tea

25:55.880 --> 25:57.190
will definitely be a big hit.

25:57.190 --> 25:59.990
The loser will be
the winner's sidekick for a week.

26:01.810 --> 26:02.850
You said it.

26:23.350 --> 26:23.960
Handsome.

26:23.960 --> 26:24.790
Come here.

26:24.790 --> 26:25.640
Can you take a look?

26:25.640 --> 26:27.920
Why can't I pay with WeChat?

26:27.920 --> 26:29.130
Take a look.

26:29.310 --> 26:31.640
Ma'am, you haven't linked your bank card.

26:31.680 --> 26:33.070
I haven't linked my bank card?

26:33.070 --> 26:34.070
Right, that's it.

26:34.400 --> 26:36.570
Then could you pay for me?

26:37.040 --> 26:38.070
-I…
-I heard that

26:38.070 --> 26:39.680
your five-star hotel

26:39.680 --> 26:41.310
puts the guest first.

26:41.310 --> 26:42.830
Guest comes first, right?

26:42.830 --> 26:44.070
Sorry. I'll do it.

26:44.520 --> 26:45.670
I'll do it.

26:46.910 --> 26:48.240
-Hello.
-I can’t pay.

26:49.160 --> 26:50.110
Thank you.

26:52.080 --> 26:52.550
Sweetie.

26:52.550 --> 26:53.880
Give me a hug.

26:55.040 --> 26:56.260
Take a look.

26:57.160 --> 26:58.240
Do I look imposing?

26:58.440 --> 27:00.260
I almost didn't recognize you.

27:01.000 --> 27:02.610
Your sister picked it for me.

27:02.640 --> 27:04.160
After all, she's

27:04.180 --> 27:05.210
been around in the big city.

27:05.210 --> 27:05.850
Right?

27:05.880 --> 27:06.880
Let me tell you,

27:06.880 --> 27:09.200
I've done my homework this time.

27:09.200 --> 27:10.440
I won't let you down.

27:10.440 --> 27:11.350
Okay. Let's go.

27:11.350 --> 27:11.920
Let's go.

27:24.240 --> 27:25.590
Slow down. Wait.

27:25.590 --> 27:27.640
You're taking the food away too fast.

27:27.640 --> 27:29.010
Just now, at the seafood section,

27:29.010 --> 27:31.640
I almost didn't get the sashimi.

27:31.680 --> 27:32.970
I'm sorry, Ma'am.

27:34.500 --> 27:35.270
Look,

27:35.270 --> 27:36.200
there's still so much left.

27:36.200 --> 27:37.110
It's a waste not to eat it.

27:37.110 --> 27:38.160
Miss,

27:38.200 --> 27:39.830
could you please help me put this

27:39.830 --> 27:40.960
on that table? That table over there.

27:40.960 --> 27:41.640
Okay.

27:41.640 --> 27:42.540
Okay.

27:43.310 --> 27:44.240
I'll hurry up and get some more.

27:44.240 --> 27:46.500
Otherwise you guys will take it all away.

28:02.730 --> 28:04.580
Have you checked her background clearly?

28:04.580 --> 28:06.550
So far, we only know
she's Xu Miyu's mother,

28:06.550 --> 28:07.610
named Jiao Xiumei.

28:07.610 --> 28:09.600
She used to farm in the countryside,

28:09.600 --> 28:11.480
and later opened
a guesthouse with her husband,

28:11.480 --> 28:13.410
but the business wasn't very good.

28:19.200 --> 28:20.170
Waiter!

28:20.810 --> 28:21.410
Waiter!

28:21.770 --> 28:22.770
Why is no one here?

28:23.620 --> 28:24.780
I know.

28:26.190 --> 28:27.180
Hold on, please.

28:27.780 --> 28:28.980
Espresso?

28:32.360 --> 28:33.160
Okay.

28:35.420 --> 28:36.270
Keep going.

28:36.290 --> 28:37.350
I can hear you guys.

28:41.150 --> 28:44.660
I want to know about
the representative pieces.

28:45.010 --> 28:45.650
Yeah.

28:54.540 --> 28:56.560
Very impressive.

29:12.030 --> 29:12.830
Why

29:13.670 --> 29:15.670
is it as bitter as Chinese medicine?

29:18.110 --> 29:19.240
This Ji Feng...

29:19.720 --> 29:20.830
Bringing a village woman

29:20.830 --> 29:23.230
to save afternoon tea
at a five-star hotel,

29:24.550 --> 29:26.810
is he taking an unconventional approach

29:26.880 --> 29:28.250
or is he out of options?

29:28.550 --> 29:30.160
I guess he has no way out.

29:30.680 --> 29:31.880
After all, we've given a heads-up

29:31.880 --> 29:33.180
to all the dessert businesses in the city.

29:33.180 --> 29:35.380
It's not that easy to hire a master chef.

29:36.960 --> 29:38.210
I hope so.

29:41.030 --> 29:43.680
We will work with local artists.

29:43.710 --> 29:47.570
But we also want to
expand into international markets.

29:47.680 --> 29:48.290
Yeah.

29:49.230 --> 29:50.400
Besides...

30:00.550 --> 30:01.590
Mom.

30:01.920 --> 30:03.530
You took so much food.

30:03.560 --> 30:04.880
Can you finish it?

30:05.240 --> 30:06.480
I can.

30:07.400 --> 30:09.700
I was in a hurry last time
I came to see you.

30:10.020 --> 30:12.060
Today I'm going to eat as much as I want.

30:12.060 --> 30:13.340
Then eat quickly.

30:13.370 --> 30:14.350
You have to come with me later.

30:14.350 --> 30:15.640
Many people in the kitchen
are waiting for you.

30:15.640 --> 30:16.960
Don't rush me.

30:16.960 --> 30:18.110
Morning, Ms. Xu.

30:19.840 --> 30:21.500
-Morning, Mr. Tan.
-Morning.

30:23.110 --> 30:23.880
This is...

30:24.110 --> 30:26.100
This, this is my mother.

30:26.130 --> 30:27.880
This is our guest, Mr. Tan.

30:27.970 --> 30:29.170
Hello, Mrs. Xu.

30:29.480 --> 30:31.610
So you can speak Chinese.

30:32.110 --> 30:34.510
He was the one
who poured me coffee just now.

30:34.550 --> 30:36.210
I heard him speaking English.

30:36.210 --> 30:37.720
I haven't had the chance to thank you yet.

30:37.720 --> 30:38.240
Thank you.

30:38.240 --> 30:39.590
It's nothing.

30:39.740 --> 30:40.400
Thank you, Mr. Tan.

30:40.400 --> 30:41.330
You're welcome.

30:41.350 --> 30:42.590
Well, take your time.

30:42.590 --> 30:43.450
I'll get going.

30:44.240 --> 30:45.240
I'm done eating too.

30:45.240 --> 30:46.310
Let's go together.

30:46.930 --> 30:47.770
It's fine.

30:47.920 --> 30:49.810
What do you mean, go together?

30:50.380 --> 30:51.400
He's a guest.

30:51.400 --> 30:53.070
Don't try to get close to him.

30:53.100 --> 30:55.510
Don't think I don't know who Mr. Tan is.

30:55.710 --> 30:57.510
Your sister told me everything.

30:58.770 --> 31:00.070
Tell me the truth.

31:00.350 --> 31:01.960
How far have you two gone?

31:01.960 --> 31:02.880
Nowhere.

31:03.880 --> 31:05.440
I think he's pretty good.

31:05.480 --> 31:06.680
He is good-looking,

31:06.680 --> 31:08.060
and capable.

31:08.160 --> 31:09.360
And he's good to you.

31:09.830 --> 31:11.030
Don't be so indifferent.

31:11.030 --> 31:12.550
Give him a chance.

31:12.550 --> 31:13.660
Mom.

31:13.680 --> 31:14.920
Let me say this to you again.

31:14.920 --> 31:16.080
This is a hotel.

31:16.100 --> 31:17.650
I'm here to work and make money,

31:17.650 --> 31:19.280
and the guests
aren't here for blind dates.

31:19.280 --> 31:20.750
Stop trying to play matchmaker,

31:20.750 --> 31:21.310
okay?

31:21.310 --> 31:22.910
Don't play innocent with me.

31:22.920 --> 31:24.720
I'm doing this for your own good.

31:24.740 --> 31:26.350
You're in your thirties.

31:26.400 --> 31:28.030
Aren't you going to find a partner?

31:28.030 --> 31:29.070
Without a family,

31:29.070 --> 31:31.550
who's going to be
with you when you're old?

31:31.590 --> 31:32.960
Think clearly about it.

31:32.960 --> 31:34.890
Mom, stop meddling in my business.

31:35.050 --> 31:36.790
There are people upstairs
waiting to assess you.

31:36.790 --> 31:38.450
Mind your own business first.

31:39.680 --> 31:41.510
Let's just live our own lives, okay?

31:41.510 --> 31:42.490
Fine.

31:42.610 --> 31:44.070
You're all grown up now,

31:44.100 --> 31:46.030
and you don't listen to me anymore.

31:46.920 --> 31:47.850
Let's get going.

31:52.550 --> 31:53.880
Chef Jiao will be here soon.

31:53.880 --> 31:55.740
So we need to hurry up.

31:57.860 --> 31:58.660
That'll do.

32:00.550 --> 32:01.390
Mr. Ji.

32:01.680 --> 32:02.960
Why are you here?

32:02.990 --> 32:04.160
Chef Jiao is visiting.

32:04.160 --> 32:06.160
Of course I have to
welcome her personally.

32:06.160 --> 32:07.240
Pleased to meet you.

32:07.240 --> 32:08.970
So you are the general manager?

32:09.750 --> 32:11.990
I've often heard Miyu talk about you.

32:12.010 --> 32:14.420
Look at this temperament and appearance.

32:15.070 --> 32:17.260
You're better than the stars on TV.

32:17.440 --> 32:18.440
General Manager.

32:18.590 --> 32:19.790
Are you married?

32:19.810 --> 32:21.680
Mom, what are you saying?

32:23.050 --> 32:23.920
It's okay.

32:24.740 --> 32:25.740
I'm still single.

32:29.290 --> 32:31.200
Then let's begin.

32:31.250 --> 32:32.600
Okay.

32:32.630 --> 32:33.690
I've prepared it for you.

32:33.690 --> 32:34.490
Okay.

32:41.160 --> 32:42.840
We have prepared some tools for you.

32:42.840 --> 32:44.570
See if they are suitable.

32:44.770 --> 32:47.480
Things in a big hotel
are truly professional.

32:47.510 --> 32:48.530
Then I'll use them.

32:48.530 --> 32:49.270
Okay.

34:23.980 --> 34:25.540
Blooming Prosperity.

34:26.580 --> 34:28.110
Abundance Year After Year.

34:28.860 --> 34:31.170
Look, this keeps the flowers fresh.

34:31.199 --> 34:31.900
Look.

34:31.920 --> 34:33.179
Right? So fresh.

34:37.540 --> 34:38.139
Mom,

34:38.520 --> 34:39.909
is your arthritis acting up again?

34:39.909 --> 34:41.840
It's nothing. Just an old problem.

34:51.179 --> 34:52.580
Come, Chef Jiao, please.

34:58.930 --> 35:00.930
This room faces south.

35:04.000 --> 35:05.960
Do I have to pay for this room?

35:06.600 --> 35:08.190
Chef Jiao, you are
the boat pastry consultant

35:08.190 --> 35:09.070
for our hotel.

35:09.280 --> 35:11.190
All food and accommodation expenses

35:11.190 --> 35:12.550
will be covered by us.

35:12.590 --> 35:13.320
You don't need to worry.

35:13.320 --> 35:14.140
Then,

35:14.360 --> 35:16.110
if I eat and stay here,

35:16.190 --> 35:17.840
will I still get paid?

35:17.930 --> 35:20.760
Mom, let's talk about the contract later.

35:20.780 --> 35:22.250
We can talk about the contract later,

35:22.250 --> 35:23.910
but we must be clear about the money.

35:23.910 --> 35:25.180
Your dad told me

35:25.210 --> 35:27.470
to ask about the money clearly in person.

35:27.510 --> 35:28.670
If the pay isn't clear,

35:28.670 --> 35:30.190
I can't start working.

35:30.190 --> 35:30.710
Right?

35:30.710 --> 35:31.670
Yes, it's fine.

35:32.070 --> 35:34.400
What is your ideal salary, Chef Jiao?

35:36.630 --> 35:38.150
7,000 a month.

35:38.170 --> 35:39.970
That's not too much, right?

35:40.230 --> 35:40.910
No problem.

35:40.930 --> 35:41.520
Okay.

35:41.650 --> 35:42.250
No.

35:42.270 --> 35:44.680
7,000 is too little.

35:44.700 --> 35:46.370
Mom, we'll discuss this later.

35:46.370 --> 35:47.370
8,000.

35:47.390 --> 35:49.850
At least 8,500.

35:50.080 --> 35:52.590
Chef Jiao, you don't
need to answer me right away.

35:52.590 --> 35:54.790
We can talk when you've thought it over.

35:58.110 --> 35:58.920
Ms. Xu,

35:59.290 --> 36:00.350
please take care of

36:00.360 --> 36:01.760
Chef Jiao's daily needs.

36:01.840 --> 36:04.280
We hope Chef Jiao
can start working immediately.

36:04.280 --> 36:06.760
We will also draft the contract
as soon as possible.

36:06.760 --> 36:07.590
When the time comes, please

36:07.590 --> 36:09.040
help Chef Jiao review it.

36:09.190 --> 36:10.550
Okay, Mr. Ji. Thank you.

36:11.730 --> 36:12.400
Right.

36:12.430 --> 36:14.060
Um, here is the room card.

36:24.490 --> 36:25.300
Get some rest.

36:34.600 --> 36:35.440
Mom.

36:36.070 --> 36:37.130
Congratulations.

36:38.860 --> 36:39.650
So?

36:39.760 --> 36:41.590
I'm quite capable, am I?

36:41.590 --> 36:42.800
Of course.

36:43.760 --> 36:45.150
Let's eat some fruit.

36:45.190 --> 36:47.080
Look how fresh it is.

36:47.360 --> 36:49.320
As expected of a five-star hotel.

36:49.320 --> 36:50.510
Here, let me wipe it for you.

36:49.640 --> 36:51.050
[Yunnan Baiyao Plaster]

36:51.940 --> 36:52.370
[Yunnan Baiyao Plaster]

37:01.360 --> 37:02.000
Rui,

37:02.630 --> 37:04.030
can Chef Jiao's contract

37:04.030 --> 37:05.320
be ready this week?

37:06.670 --> 37:09.320
There are a bunch of contracts lined up.

37:09.440 --> 37:11.630
First come, first served, okay?

37:11.670 --> 37:13.800
The afternoon tea project is urgent.

37:13.800 --> 37:15.060
Please prioritize it.

37:19.850 --> 37:22.760
It seems that what's urgent,
aside from afternoon tea,

37:22.760 --> 37:23.960
is someone's eagerness

37:23.960 --> 37:26.320
to show goodwill with an ulterior motive.

37:26.630 --> 37:27.400
What?

37:28.000 --> 37:29.400
Haven't apologized yet?

37:30.590 --> 37:31.190
I have.

37:32.360 --> 37:33.960
Then that's it.

37:34.510 --> 37:35.910
But she didn't accept it.

37:40.280 --> 37:41.550
Xu Miyu?

37:42.430 --> 37:43.890
Actually, I'm quite glad.

37:43.900 --> 37:44.930
She was willing to tell me

37:44.930 --> 37:46.860
that she didn't accept my apology.

37:49.320 --> 37:50.550
Glad?

37:51.760 --> 37:54.760
Telling the truth
is always better than holding it in.

37:54.760 --> 37:58.000
This way, I know what I should do.

38:02.480 --> 38:03.280
Feng,

38:03.900 --> 38:04.920
are you okay?

38:06.070 --> 38:07.150
The contract.

38:07.440 --> 38:09.370
Remember to give it to me this week.

38:10.010 --> 38:10.860
Okay.

38:16.170 --> 38:16.790
[Statement Regarding the Reception
of VIP Guest Mr. Ma Wenhui]

38:16.820 --> 38:17.430
[During my reception of Mr. Ma Wenhui,]

38:17.450 --> 38:18.040
[my attitude caused him
an unpleasant experience.]

38:18.060 --> 38:18.560
[I hereby submit this statement.]

38:18.580 --> 38:19.310
[Submitted by Lu Xiaoyan]

38:25.440 --> 38:27.040
I understand the situation.

38:27.110 --> 38:27.670
Learn from this.

38:27.670 --> 38:29.130
Don't let it happen again.

38:29.500 --> 38:32.000
Don't think I'm
scared of you because of this.

38:32.000 --> 38:33.860
I don't need you to be scared of me.

38:36.900 --> 38:38.480
These are the Western restaurant's
newly launched

38:38.480 --> 38:39.830
afternoon tea boat pastries.

38:39.830 --> 38:41.420
You've all worked hard
these past couple of days.

38:41.420 --> 38:42.540
Try them.

38:55.740 --> 38:57.050
They look so nice.

38:57.080 --> 38:58.510
Then eat them yourself.

38:59.100 --> 39:00.360
Then I won't be polite.

39:02.140 --> 39:04.500
[Blooming Prosperity]

39:02.320 --> 39:03.480
What is this?

39:03.480 --> 39:04.630
This is also our specialty.

39:04.530 --> 39:07.320
[Abundance Year After Year]

39:04.630 --> 39:06.640
I'll take both then.

39:06.760 --> 39:07.890
Sure, wait a moment.

39:27.050 --> 39:28.370
[Employment Contract]

39:28.480 --> 39:31.830
[Work content] [Reward]

39:31.360 --> 39:33.290
20,000? So high?

39:33.400 --> 39:35.320
Mom, your boat pastries became a hit
in our Western restaurant

39:35.320 --> 39:37.630
in just one afternoon.

39:37.670 --> 39:38.730
Really?

39:42.220 --> 39:43.320
I've never had so much money

39:43.320 --> 39:45.760
in my pocket my whole life.

39:47.380 --> 39:48.900
Now I see it clearly.

39:49.210 --> 39:50.830
That Mr. Ji

39:50.960 --> 39:52.510
probably has his eye on you.

39:52.510 --> 39:53.920
Mom, what nonsense are you talking about?

39:53.920 --> 39:54.930
Otherwise,

39:54.950 --> 39:57.070
why would he pay an old lady like me

39:57.070 --> 39:58.510
such a high salary?

39:58.550 --> 40:00.190
It's called a consulting fee.

40:00.190 --> 40:01.320
Whatever fee it is,

40:01.340 --> 40:02.990
he is doing it to please you.

40:03.960 --> 40:04.960
This is the result of a joint assessment

40:04.960 --> 40:05.710
by the HR Department,

40:05.710 --> 40:07.150
the Administration Department,

40:07.150 --> 40:08.800
and the Business Management Department.

40:08.800 --> 40:10.260
It's not just his call.

40:10.290 --> 40:11.110
Besides,

40:11.110 --> 40:12.230
you should have some confidence

40:12.230 --> 40:13.630
in your own skills, okay?

40:14.550 --> 40:16.960
You are the one
who should have confidence.

40:17.000 --> 40:18.880
When have I ever been wrong?

40:18.880 --> 40:20.880
The way he looks at you is different.

40:23.310 --> 40:24.590
Mr. Tan

40:24.620 --> 40:26.190
and Mr. Ji.

40:26.210 --> 40:27.810
Both seem like good catches.

40:27.940 --> 40:29.340
Which one do you like more?

40:29.340 --> 40:30.220
While I'm here,

40:30.240 --> 40:31.730
I'll help you pull some strings.

40:31.730 --> 40:34.450
Mom, stop dreaming, will you?

40:35.080 --> 40:36.150
I understand your anxiety

40:36.150 --> 40:37.440
about having an older,

40:37.480 --> 40:39.360
divorced daughter.

40:39.380 --> 40:40.410
But that's your problem.

40:40.410 --> 40:41.500
It has nothing to do with me.

40:41.500 --> 40:42.670
And it certainly has nothing to do

40:42.670 --> 40:44.320
with Mr. Tan and Mr. Ji.

40:44.340 --> 40:47.140
One is my guest,

40:47.170 --> 40:48.440
and making sure he's not disturbed

40:48.440 --> 40:49.320
is my job.

40:49.320 --> 40:51.630
The other is my boss.

40:51.760 --> 40:53.630
He could easily get us both fired

40:53.630 --> 40:55.110
by lifting a finger.

40:55.130 --> 40:57.420
They are not from the same world as me.

40:57.450 --> 40:58.400
Do you understand?

40:58.400 --> 41:00.760
What... what are you talking about?

41:00.800 --> 41:01.360
Alright, alright.

41:01.360 --> 41:02.280
Just focus on work

41:02.280 --> 41:03.570
right now.

41:03.590 --> 41:06.450
There's no problem with the contract.
Just sign it.

41:07.000 --> 41:08.240
So stubborn.

41:11.030 --> 41:12.030
Where do I sign?

41:23.070 --> 41:24.320
Duan,

41:24.320 --> 41:25.780
hurry up.

41:25.930 --> 41:27.570
There are still pots to wash.

41:32.240 --> 41:33.400
The water's barely running.

41:33.400 --> 41:34.930
How can you wash them clean?

41:38.850 --> 41:41.040
Li Qiaoqi, don't go too far.

41:42.460 --> 41:44.570
Getting mad already?

41:45.180 --> 41:46.690
You made the bet yourself.

41:46.720 --> 41:48.120
You must accept the loss.

41:48.860 --> 41:50.120
You don't really think

41:50.150 --> 41:51.920
that just by improving the afternoon tea,

41:51.920 --> 41:53.570
Purong can turn the tables, do you?

41:53.570 --> 41:55.190
The best is yet to come.

42:05.550 --> 42:07.550
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

42:07.910 --> 42:09.770
Purong's dishes are too fragile.

42:09.820 --> 42:10.570
Pay for it.

42:22.250 --> 42:24.180
It's not like I can't afford to pay.

42:36.800 --> 42:39.130
The contract is signed. Thank you, Mr. Ji.

42:43.840 --> 42:45.300
You don't need to thank me.

42:45.480 --> 42:46.760
Your mother's willingness to entrust

42:46.760 --> 42:48.090
this craft to Purong Hotel

42:48.090 --> 42:49.380
is our fortune.

42:52.440 --> 42:53.770
[You don't need to thank me.
Your mother's willingness to entrust]

42:53.790 --> 42:55.650
[this craft to Purong Hotel
is our fortune.]

43:03.120 --> 43:07.280
[Xu Miyu]

43:07.710 --> 43:09.440
If you must thank me,

43:10.670 --> 43:11.590
how about

43:12.710 --> 43:14.000
we have dinner together?
